cline in the fraction of bulges in high-$z$ galaxies (with an\nassociated drop in BH accretion). JWST and Origins will resolve the discrepancy\nbetween our predicted BHAD and the X-ray results by constraining Compton-thick\nAGN and bulge evolution at high redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Aug 2021 21:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-24"}
