alized finance ecosystem, and our approach can act as a whistleblower\nthat identifies scam tokens at their early stages.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 08:09:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2021 08:08:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-12"}
