. Next, we present detailed\ncase studies of the dynamics of problematic speech in a far-right Facebook\ngroup, exemplifying its mutation from conservative to extreme. Finally, we\nexamine the dynamics of opinion emergence and co-occurrence, and we hint at\nsome pathways through which extreme opinions creep into the mainstream online\ndiscourse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 11:01:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Apr 2022 03:30:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 May 2022 01:55:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-05"}
