, the thermopower shows an\nanomalous peak around the superconducting transition on the hole side and\npoints towards the possible role of enhanced superconducting fluctuations in\nMtBLG.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2021 12:52:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Sep 2021 03:38:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
